{"tid":1126222,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[奇難雜症]屋企部機裝唔到win10 就算裝到都只會正常用到1日","createTime":"2019-04-26T08:33:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T13:06:10.000Z","uid":91685,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"bcc2a88a656fe1b9a1ad7579d7dd9f01f6f7ddcd","tid":1126222,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:33:39.000Z","msg":"hardware如下<br />\nasrock b85m-hds<br />\ni5-4440<br />\nadata 8gb ram<br />\nantec hcg520w<br />\n死雞 1tb<br />\n<br />\n當時係岩岩出左i5 4代<br />\n咁我就買左呢部機裝win7 一直都正常<br />\n冇幾耐就自動升左上win10 咁都係一直正常冇問題 但係覺得部機唔太順 就自己整左隻usb手指重裝win10<br />\n之後問題就黎 裝完只係用到1日左右 之後部機會開始不定時hang機 但仲係入到win10 <br />\n再過幾日就會hang係下面呢個位 windows都入唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/THUaWdN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTHUaWdN.jpg&h=df454b3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(網上偷既圖)<br />\n<br />\n最後我換左msi b85m-e45重裝win10先冇問題 咁我以為係塊asrock問題<br />\n<br />\n呢幾日有fd換機 咁我就執左佢粒i7同hd 換完之後又開始有上面個問題<br />\n我諗應該係換過硬件driver唔夾 咁就重裝win10<br />\n插usb 裝完之後reboot就disk read error occurred 再試埋我fd隻WD hd裝 用diskpart clean哂全部再裝都係咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JoGpgdU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJoGpgdU.jpg&h=7a18a856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n(網上偷既圖)<br />\n<br />\n之後我跟網上D方法試過哂都係唔得(boot pe rebuild mgr, diskpart set active, bios轉legacy/uefi)<br />\n<br />\n搞左幾日都係咁 最後拎左隻hd返公司試 即刻得左入到win10<br />\n<br />\n到底係咩問題 係咪真係我屋企部機柒D裝唔到win10?"},{"pid":"54446f03f8ec6dd555ed92a1d12a1cbd14ce5fd1","tid":1126222,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:34:22.000Z","msg":"真心求教到底係咩問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61137bc104788b16d5add9a2852c5d8d82abac5","tid":1126222,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"Driver問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba963cc9ac80a594b8b67d20dd510ab1e0eb2f7","tid":1126222,"uid":228846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔考慮係種嘅問題"},{"pid":"5fc3cb02e6b0fdb3b13a7f1ad368264346817e5d","tid":1126222,"uid":91685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b61137bc104788b16d5add9a2852c5d8d82abac5","tid":1126222,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"Driver問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:41:38.000Z","msg":"但而家windows都未裝完 只係copy完資料reboot 之後應該係黑畫面轉轉下等佢裝埋 我係入唔到呢到 copy完資料就彈disk read error occurred"},{"pid":"7a813dd22b17f445466826843ee253c7886d32b2","tid":1126222,"uid":91685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bba963cc9ac80a594b8b67d20dd510ab1e0eb2f7","tid":1126222,"uid":228846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔考慮係種嘅問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"隻iso係上microsoft官網dl既 當時用asrock都係即dl即整<br />\n到今次都係即dl即整 冇理由咁岩掛<br />\n同埋我拎返公司boot得入window"},{"pid":"62ee9f953dbf6491465eaac17f9c8da9de45de53","tid":1126222,"uid":94501,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:46:05.000Z","msg":"火牛問題?"},{"pid":"1b6b06001d3ebfc582271437b9d2747c1e7dd5b1","tid":1126222,"uid":228846,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7a813dd22b17f445466826843ee253c7886d32b2","tid":1126222,"uid":91685,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bba963cc9ac80a594b8b67d20dd510ab1e0eb2f7","tid":1126222,"uid":228846,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:39:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔考慮係種嘅問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:44:41.000Z","msg":"隻iso係上microsoft官網dl既 當時用asrock都係即dl即整<br />\n到今次都係即dl即整 冇理由咁岩掛<br />\n同埋我拎返公司boot得入window"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T08:48:08.000Z","msg":"鳩估可能關bios事<